text: Józef Rajnisz (born 3 March 1932) is a Polish gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1932 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Poland Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Bytom
